HEADWORD: Traveled
<hw>Trav"eled</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having made
journeys; having gained knowledge or experience by traveling; hence,
knowing; experienced.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>travelled</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The <qex>traveled</qex> thane, Athenian Aberdeen.</q>
<rj><qau>Byron.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Traveler</ent>⟦br⟧
